{
  "text": "Membrane-enriched cell extracts and western blotting were performed as described previously [CITATION_1] . ScMep2 protein was probed with a rabbit antiserum (1:1000) raised against the Cterminal region of the proteins [CITATION_2] . HsRhCG was probed with an anti-HsRhCG antibody (1:1000; SantaCruz). HsRhAG and HsRhCG proteins tagged to GFP were probed with anti-GFP (1:5000) antibody, and ScPma1 and ScDpm1 proteins with antiPma1 (1:10000) [CITATION_3] and anti-Dpm1 (1:5000) (Molecular Probes) antibodies. Primary antibodies were detected with horseradishperoxidase-conjugated anti-rabbit and anti-mouse-IgG secondary antibodies followed by measurement of chemoluminescence (Lumi-Light PLUS , Roche).",
